{"tid":1521790,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（1848）金鐘MTR D空氣有事，自己睇住","createTime":"2019-08-31T10:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T10:56:56.000Z","uid":230692,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e2915e4ed0237e01cc40af66f72f008eb3b620eb","tid":1521790,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:49:12.000Z","msg":"金鐘MTR D空氣有事，明顯係催淚煙，深到去南港島線都聞到，好在係唔太多。各位唔理係唔係發夢，自己都要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056a2c0a1b3c739867523d45610054909c0228b1","tid":1521790,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:50:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29e1cc1a1c918d566c07febb96e1012a54f09958","tid":1521790,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:50:58.000Z","msg":"［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal"},{"pid":"37fe30363bd8fd59fdf6634b70165fdc4eb68bf4","tid":1521790,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:51:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dac91538e4f3066f29b88dacaf46897f130bbddc","tid":1521790,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"1845 現場手足報料：「啱啱試過含酒精濕紙巾可抹走顏色水」<br />\n幫忙廣傳"},{"pid":"49faeddcb47b0c19ceaaade1f5a4c257001d6694","tid":1521790,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:51:57.000Z","msg":"顏色水點搞自己係度講埋，兄弟們小心<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"e7e54ac77709a59a89a7c4c8a48db4f238f8c974","tid":1521790,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d16c43075c7bf4a7484bfcd19c6e8f0d591c23fc","tid":1521790,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35f2216c9b385d54c5158814a7bf44ad39494cec","tid":1521790,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:52:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e97f5e3d6d23ef089f184cf1d3000686373a2c7","tid":1521790,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">830 大濫捕 黑警被斬 完全將焦點轉移<br />\n<br />\n提提大家 我地今日出黎目的係<br />\n<br />\n因為5年前831中共就普選設下「提名委員會」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">還我真普選！<br />\n<br />\nBe Water</span></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"45a0eba6501c356b34bf6fa305cc4ffdbc5dfd35","tid":1521790,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49faeddcb47b0c19ceaaade1f5a4c257001d6694","tid":1521790,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:51:57.000Z","msg":"顏色水點搞自己係度講埋，兄弟們小心<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:53:51.000Z","msg":"梳打粉+水 /落妝液"},{"pid":"75f2161028efebe4b5b6969156897aff7dcd531f","tid":1521790,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:54:23.000Z","msg":"黨鐵員工表示無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2ab1378a52431aba875bdd9369581d06ee35b5","tid":1521790,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:20.000Z","msg":"地區的兒子需要接送<br />\n<br />\n要拖鞋換 小心螢光鞋底路<br />\n<br />\nGASTBY 冰紙巾好似抹到"},{"pid":"8259c39e224778a9cc8d5d428560d0a00e3522c1","tid":1521790,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:36.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f78d6d4d19e1f5c61b81bee26688546e2029a2de","tid":1521790,"uid":230692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"小心"}]}